Package: ucrData
Title: Retrieve and Parse Supplementary Homicide Reports (SHR) Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Julio", "Trecenti", , "julio.trecenti@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1680-6389")),
    person("Ivan", "Ribeiro", , "iribeiro@unifesp.br", role = "aut"),
    person("CEOE-Unifesp", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Provides tools to download, extract, and parse Supplementary Homicide Reports (SHR) data from the FBI's Uniform Crime Reporting (UCR) program. It includes functions to automate fetching data for specific years, handling fixed-width file formats, and loading data into tidy R structures for analysis.
